722
00:58:10,260 --> 00:58:11,490
Ya, Hae Jun?

723
00:58:13,159 --> 00:58:15,129
Jangan datang, Tae Seok.

724
00:58:16,599 --> 00:58:17,800
Jangan datang.

725
00:58:19,869 --> 00:58:21,230
Kamu kenapa?

726
00:58:21,500 --> 00:58:23,869
Aku tidak menyesal

727
00:58:25,040 --> 00:58:26,510
bertemu denganmu, Tae Seok.

728
00:58:26,970 --> 00:58:29,909
Itu bukan salahmu, Tae Seok.

729
00:58:30,510 --> 00:58:32,040
Lupakan segalanya.

730
00:58:34,980 --> 00:58:37,349
Kamu sudah kesulitan

731
00:58:39,990 --> 00:58:42,619
selama 13 tahun terakhir.

732
00:58:42,990 --> 00:58:45,119
Tahanlah sebentar lagi. Aku dalam perjalanan ke sana.

733
00:58:45,119 --> 00:58:46,359
Di mana kamu sekarang?

734
00:58:47,030 --> 00:58:48,690
Aku merindukanmu.

735
00:58:58,540 --> 00:58:59,710
Hae Jun?

736
00:59:00,710 --> 00:59:01,970
Hae Jun.

737
00:59:04,210 --> 00:59:05,649
Hae Jun!

738
00:59:26,930 --> 00:59:28,329
Pria ini mabuk!

739
00:59:28,329 --> 00:59:30,240
